{{zh-forms|[[东西]]|[[東西]]}}
==Mandarin==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|[ tʊŋ˥˥ɕi ]}}

====Etymology====
Literally, the two [[morpheme]]s that compose this word mean ''east'' and ''west''

===Noun===
{{cmn-noun|p|pint=dong1xi|tra=東西|sim=东西}}
 
# [[something]]; [[thing]]

===Usage notes===
*'''dōngxi''' means thing in a physical sense, whereas [[shìqing]] means thing in an abstract sense.

===See also===
*[[dōngxī]] ''east and west''
